      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/ff867924-a507-11e2-a553-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  No failures.",
